==Arabic==
===Etymology===
From {{ARchar|زيت}} (''záyyata''), to [[oil]], to [[lubricate]], to [[grease]].

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|زيت}}''' (zayt) {{m}}, {{ARchar|[[زيوت]]}} (zuyūt) {{p}}

# [[oil]] ''(all types of oil, edible, fuel, motor oil, etc.)''

